  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Coding Instructor",
  "description": "<p>We are seeking an experienced and passionate Coding Teacher to join our team! As a Coding Teacher, you will be responsible for designing and delivering high-quality coding lessons to students of various ages and skill levels.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<p>- Deliver engaging coding lessons to students</p>\n<p>- Implement curriculum for coding programs</p>\n<p>- Provide individualized support and feedback to students</p>\n<p>- Collaborate with other teachers to integrate coding into the broader curriculum</p>\n<p>- Participate in staff development and training to stay current with industry trends and best practices</p>\n<p>- Communicate with parents and guardians about student progress</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<p>- Bachelor's degree in Computer Science, Education, or related field</p>\n<p>- Proven experience teaching coding to students of various ages and skill levels</p>\n<p>- Strong knowledge of programming languages such as Python, Java, and JavaScript</p>\n<p>- Excellent communication and interpersonal skills</p>\n<p>- Ability to work independently and as part of a team</p>\n<p>- Familiarity with educational technology and coding platforms</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>*Nice to Have:*</p>\n<p>- Master's degree in Computer Science, Education, or related field</p>\n<p>- Experience in teaching</p>\n<p>- Familiarity with agile development methodologies</p>\n<p>- Experience working with students with diverse learning needs</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>*What We Offer:*</p>\n<p>- Competitive salary and benefits package</p>\n<p>- Opportunities for professional development and growth</p>\n<p>- Collaborative and dynamic work environment</p>\n<p>- The chance to make a positive impact on the lives of students</p>",
